No. 11-6938. Steven J. Smith, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 1046, 132 S. Ct. 600,

181 L. Ed. 2d 442,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8214. November 14, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied. Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 433 Fed. Appx. 891.
